events.body:
Silent payments was removed as priority project in the last irc meeting and replaced with the legacy wallet removal without asking the silent payment voters if they would like to recast their votes.

If I'm counting correctly, there were 25 voters of which 18 used all three of their votes, including all 10 silent payment voters. This means that the outcome of the vote could be quite different if these votes would be recast.

@fjahr @josibake @achow101 @pinheadmz @theStack @ismaelsadeeq @S3RK @furszy @hernanmarino @BrandonOdiwuor you are the SP voters and should recast your third vote or indicate that you are willing to drop it.
